    "Its objective is to furnish explanations for the knowledge-based question-answering task within CommonsenseQA, providing an in-depth comprehension of the general attributes linked to various options.",
    "• HEAD-QA (Vilares and Gómez-Rodríguez, 2019).",
    "The HEAD-QA dataset encompasses a variety of multiple-choice questions and answers, spanning disciplines such as medicine, pharmacology, psychology, nursing, biology, and chemistry.",
    "The questions are sourced from professional position exams within the Spanish healthcare system, adding a level of complexity.",
    "The dataset is available in both English and Spanish versions, covering a range of technical and societal knowledge."
